@startuml "Ionosense HPC - One Slide Summary"
!theme plain

' ---- styling ----
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam titleFontSize 28
skinparam rectangleBorderThickness 4
skinparam arrowThickness 5
skinparam roundCorner 30
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam rectangleShadowing true
hide stereotype

' ---- color macros (names won't collide with labels) ----
!define CLR_PROBLEM   FF6B6B
!define CLR_SOLUTION  4ECDC4
!define CLR_IMPACT    95E77E
!define CLR_HILITE    FFE66D

title <b>Ionosense HPC</b>\n<font size="20">GPU-Accelerated Platform for Ionospheric Research</font>

' ============================================================================
' Problem — Solution — Impact
' ============================================================================

rectangle "**THE PROBLEM**\n\n<b>Ionospheric Analysis Bottleneck</b>\n\n• Months of data → weeks of processing\n• No real-time capability\n• Limited hypothesis testing\n• Reproducibility challenges" as Problem <<Challenge>> #CLR_PROBLEM

rectangle "**OUR SOLUTION**\n\n<b>GPU-Accelerated Research Platform</b>\n\n• <font size=\"22\"><b>100–1000× faster</b></font>\n• Real-time processing (<100μs)\n• Automated workflows\n• Full reproducibility" as Solution <<Platform>> #CLR_SOLUTION

rectangle "**THE IMPACT**\n\n<b>Accelerated Scientific Discovery</b>\n\n• <font size=\"22\"><b>2 weeks → 1 hour</b></font>\n• More experiments\n• Faster publications\n• New discoveries" as Impact <<Results>> #CLR_IMPACT

Problem -right-> Solution : <font size="20"><b>solve with</b></font>
Solution -right-> Impact  : <font size="20"><b>achieve</b></font>

' ============================================================================
' Key Numbers Banner
' ============================================================================
note top of Solution #CLR_HILITE
<b><font size="24">KEY PERFORMANCE</font></b>
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
<font size="20"><b>>10,000 FPS</b> | <b>25 GB/s</b> | <b><100μs latency</b></font>
end note

' ============================================================================
' Research Areas
' ============================================================================
together {
  rectangle "**Scintillation\nAnalysis**"   as App1 <<Application>> #F0F8FF
  rectangle "**Space Weather\nMonitoring**" as App2 <<Application>> #F0F8FF
  rectangle "**GNSS Signal\nIntegrity**"    as App3 <<Application>> #F0F8FF
}

Solution --> App1
Solution --> App2
Solution --> App3

' ============================================================================
' Bottom Line
' ============================================================================
note bottom of Impact #FFFFFF
<b><font size="24" color="#2E7D32">Ready to Accelerate Your Research?</font></b>\n
<font size="16">✅ Production Ready  ✅ Open Source  ✅ Full Support</font>
end note

@enduml
